  "prompt": "Can we swallow fenugreek seeds as a whole?",
  "response": "Yes, you can swallow fenugreek seeds whole, but it's generally better to soak or grind them for better digestion and nutrient absorption. Swallowing them whole may make it more difficult for your body to break them down and absorb their nutrients. Soaking the seeds in water overnight can also help soften them, making them easier to consume and digest. If you have any concerns or specific health conditions, it\u2019s a good idea to consult with a healthcare professional before adding new supplements to your diet.",
